import store from "@/store/store.js";
import axios from "axios";
import Router from "vue-router";

export default {
  name: "ToolbarLTC",
  data() {
    return {};

  mounted() {},
  methods: {
    logout() {
      this.$store.dispatch("logout");
      this.$router.replace({ name: "login" });
    }
  }
};
</script>
